@node "Introduction" "Introduction"

@{b}Introduction@{ub}


@{b}GuitarChord (v1.0)@{ub} is a small arexx/muirexx program that shows
graphically  the  fingerings  of guitar chords chosen by the user.  As
far  as I know, there is no other Amiga program that does the same, so
I thought it would be useful to those of us who learn and play guitar.
@endnode
